nodes.text: Graffiti was a type of vandalism, in which a being etched messages on public property. The Mandalorian Sabine Wren was a graffiti artist who regularly spray-painted Imperial buildings after committing acts of sabotage.
The starbird symbol was her signature graffiti. Her personal explosives were designed to create graffiti and she often used her airbrushes to vandalize stormtrooper armor.
